Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:08.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}普特利麦奥斯简报室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于Celestial Being在锡兰岛上的武力干预
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了148名尊贵的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然Celestial Being主张根除纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其行为只能说是扰乱国家秩序的恐怖活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类革新联盟要以坚决的态度来挑战他们的恐怖行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  由于我们的所为  人革联的军备增强了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们准备那么做的话  那我们就只有继续武力干预
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  只有这才是Celestial Being的本愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:01:00.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  为了不让Celestial Being的暴行继续下去  联合…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球化石燃料枯竭的公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用三个国家群所建造的三个轨道电梯和太阳光发电系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类甚至获得了半永久性的能源供给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  各国军队为了自己的威信和繁荣  而继续着大范围的战争游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  虽然已是24世纪  但人类依然没有统一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推翻腐朽的人们出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有MS Gundam的私立武装组织——Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为了让世界没有纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而展开了超越民族  国家  宗教的作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赋予Gundam Meister的新任务又要再次展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:11.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}#04 对外交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖活动终于蔓延到市中心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在温和派采取行动之前  推进改革…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了重振这个曾依赖于化石燃料的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有期待拥有太阳光发电系统的国家群的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我国并未参加轨道电梯的建设计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不具有能量供给权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在致富之源的石油的输出受限制的如今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会有国家肯无偿地援助我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为了寻求援助  议会才会恢复君主制度并推崇我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要做的就只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  情况可是愈发紧迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若国内继续照这样慌乱下去  那他们不久便会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武装组织——Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过没  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真IRA的活动停止声明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那份声明中虽然也有赞赏我们的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是临时性的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是害怕武力干预而先采取了行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有我们  那他们会马上重新开始活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  根除纷争并不是那么简单就能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  该休息时要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会忙起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现长久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此而存在的…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革联  总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam交过手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否毫无保留地告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  就我个人的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上并不存在能与那称作Gundam的机体抗衡的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么厉害的性能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是我的个人意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  叫你过来是对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  要把Gundam弄到手  先于联合和AEU啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要新设立专门部队  人员由你来挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一个士兵得麻烦你照顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超人机关技术研究所派来的超兵1号——苏摩·佩丽丝少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令  难不成是那个计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在水面下继续着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高层将其视作对抗Gundam的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天于中校的专门部队就职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也太年轻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不会吧  是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错  你还记得我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  他是住隔壁的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清荣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包和各部关节的强化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体表面的耐射线涂层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器选购的是Iris公司试制的新型来复枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壮观  教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  即使是启动反重力系统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全速旋转时也会受到12倍的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说是正如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这就是中尉的Flag吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德·梅森准尉  达利尔·道奇上士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应格拉哈姆·艾卡中尉的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来对Gundam调查队就职
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪比特  白天的新闻看过没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有评论员说  把Celestial Being任命为世界警察如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:20.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}联合  总统宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像联合国  无需维持费用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分人都心中有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会有人和他们联手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统  有报告称塔利比亚将于明天发表声明…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀  告诉我你的预测…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的预测一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对计划有12种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论选哪一种  我们的立场都很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道是这样  也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  刚才塔利比亚发表了声明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是塔利比亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合虽然采用的是超过50的国家议会制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:25.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是拥有太阳能分配权的美国一国的独裁体制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪比特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去举行联合的特别议会  并召集主要国家代表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们塔利比亚共和国要脱离联合  主张独自的能源使用权
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:38.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革联  国家主席府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若本主张遭到反对  并受到他国的政治  军事压力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:44.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}AEU中央议会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我国将以军事力量进行对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国坚决反对卑劣的美国支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亚有动作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个国家以前就有很强的反美意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但居然要脱离联合  并单方面主张能源权利…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想为下一轮选举做铺垫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道电梯周围国家形势的恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给太阳光发电系统的运营造成障碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合一定会接受美国的要求并下决心采取军事干涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而塔利比亚也一定预测到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉  你知道塔利比亚为何会采取这样的强行策略吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若联合采取军事行动  那Celestial Being会出来干预吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被引诱出来吗  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想说塔利比亚打算利用Celestial Being吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以能持以那种充满恐吓的强硬态度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为塔利比亚位于轨道电梯附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我国不同  有牌可使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being真的会出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  说不定本国的未来\N会因Celestial Being如何应对塔利比亚而改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本国的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说可以利用他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道是被利用  我们仍然会行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这才是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络Gundam Meister他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合因议会中多数成员的赞成  而决定向塔利比亚派遣军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  美国将独自派兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆  进入干预行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  刹那·F·清荣  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要和Gundam交手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这台特装型Flag到底能和Gundam周旋多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  无论如何都有必要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的舰队和美军第二舰队抵达塔利比亚近海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}太平洋  塔利比亚近海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西的驻军基地也调用了空中兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要掌握塔利比亚主要城市的制空权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塔利比亚军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}塔利比亚军  陆军用MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三个主要城市集结了陆军用MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可谓一触即发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  要如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已定好了  我们要做的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  Gundam出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Blue Shark  目测确认了两台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝着首都方向去  请采取应对措施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信被妨碍了  是Gundam干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:35.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}塔利比亚  首相府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首相  Celestial Being出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam散开了  估计分别是朝着三个主要城市去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要武力干预吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以联合和我们美军为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若Celestial Being进行武力干预
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有助于塔利比亚的强硬态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来  若不进行武力干预  而允许联合的军事行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他们的根除纷争的行动理念就瓦解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要选哪一个呢  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being会采取何种武力干预呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合先采取了攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可什么都还没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的创始人——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格在声明中已说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being将放任战争的国家也作为武力干预的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定塔利比亚为放任战争的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  开始干预行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  对目标进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然利用别人  太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这是单方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam开始对塔利比亚军展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam对我军展开了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热线联系布赖恩总统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是将贵国视为引起纷争的存在而展开攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他们的行动表示遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  若能撤销脱离联合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们很乐意为保护贵国而派遣军队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军为了保护身为友好国家的塔利比亚共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Celestial Being展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国的MS部队出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预料的一样  推测是为防卫塔利比亚的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照任务  各Gundam开始撤退  向安全圈撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机体接近Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美军的Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美军？  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正以普通机两倍以上的速度猛追Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Flag是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能和Gundam交手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对得不错  总统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特装型Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想过过招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  竟然还能在水中行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛用性太高了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  居然攻击塔利比亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亚还有美国好像都预测到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到Celestial Being武力干预的塔利比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先借用了美军的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  塔利比亚国内的反美情绪便会消退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而可开展美国主导的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亚的现政权也因得到美国的援助而得以稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他国家也会避免重蹈塔利比亚的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会采用露骨的反美政策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因这一系列的事件而受惠最多的是哪一方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若还不清楚的话  那你就没有资格挽救本国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦王国第一公主——玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  是怎么回事啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being攻击了塔利比亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国家不是没进行什么战争或其它事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说要让人们放弃战争  却又引起了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界可没那么简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  并不简单…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在低轨道平台的相遇  让阿里路亚想起了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧  Kyrios  在生命消逝之前
